<HEADLINE> Major Chinese Cities Enjoy Good Air Quality </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, August 7 (Xinhua) -- The latest reports released by
the China Environmental Monitoring Center indicate that the
country's major cities had good air quality during the past week.
</P>
<P>
Eleven cities -- Qingdao, Yantai, Nanning, Wenzhou, Guilin,
Zhuhai, Haikou, Xiamen, Zhanjiang, Beihai and Ningbo -- recorded
excellent air quality July 31 to August 6, according to the report.
