<HEADLINE> Evacuation Underway For Possible Diversion of Yangtze Floods </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WUHAN, August 7 (Xinhua) -- Cattle, bearing marks by their
owners, furniture, electric home appliances, and other belongings
of local residents are being moved away at a local ferry in
Gong'an County, in central China's Hubei Province.
