than 50 civilians have been killed and hundreds of others injured
in Pakistan-held Kashmir area during the last week as a result of
"India's unprovoked and indiscriminate firing across LoC which
separates the disputed region.
</P>
<P>
The armies of the two rival neighbors, positioned eye ball to
eye ball, are reported to be using weapons ranging from mortars to
heavy and light machine guns in the clashes which, according to
estimates by the media, have displaced about 20,000 people from
the bordering villages on the Pakistani side.
