<HEADLINE> Milosevic Calls for Continued Dialogue to Settle Kosovo Crisis </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BELGRADE, August 6 (Xinhua) -- Yugoslav President Slobodan
Milosevic said here Thursday that political dialogue should be
continued so as to settle the Kosovo crisis.
</P>
<P>
He made the remarks while meeting with visiting Russian Deputy
Foreign Minister Nikola Afanasjevski.
</P>
<P>
He said the international community should condemn activities
of the ethnic Albanian terrorists in Kosovo, adding that ethnic
equality was the only way to solve the issue.
</P>
<P>
Both sides agreed to settle the Kosovo crisis through political
means. 
</P>
</TEXT>
