<DOCNO> XIE19980807.0212 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-08-07 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Shanghai Stock Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, August 7 (Xinhua) -- The Composite Stock Index on the
Shanghai Stock Exchange finished at 1,271.06 points today, down
23.09 points from the previous session, according to the Guangfa
Securities Co. Ltd.
</P>
<P>
The SSE-30 index, based on 30 blue chips selected from more
than 400 A shares for domestic investors on the Shanghai Stock
Exchange, closed at 3,215.13 points, down 51.29 points from the
previous session.
</P>
<P>
A Share Index: 1,353.31 points, down 24.38 points.
</P>
<P>
B Share Index: 28.61 points, down 0.98 point.
</P>
<P>
Total Turnover: 4,647,071,000 yuan.
</P>
<P>
Total Volume:  567,622,700 shares. 
