<HEADLINE> URGENT: 30 Killed in Bus Accident North of Islamabad </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, August 7 (Xinhua) -- At least 30 people including
17 army men were killed Friday morning in a bus accident in
Shinkiyari area,  about 150 kilometers north of Islamabad.
</P>
<P>
According to initial reports, the bus heading for Rawalpindi
was negotiating a turn when it fell into a deep ravine at around 5
a.m.
</P>
<P>
Rescue operations are now under way. 
</P>
